1. *Pomalo* smo se zbunili. (We were a bit confused.)
2. Pripremamo *pomalo* drugačiju večeru. (We are preparing a slightly different dinner.)
3. *Pomalo* smo se iznenadili. (We were somewhat surprised.)
4. On je *pomalo* čudan. (He is a bit strange.)
5. *Pomalo* smo se uplašili. (We were somewhat scared.)
6. Zašto si *pomalo* tih? (Why are you a bit quiet?)
7. *Pomalo* smo se izgubili. (We got a bit lost.)
8. *Pomalo* smo se oduševili. (We were somewhat delighted.)